  overview_paragraphs = '["The It operations & support Advisory service reviews your current state, surfaces priority gaps, and leaves you with evidence-led recommendations stakeholders can act on. This assessment maps operations maturity and returns prioritised improvements your IT leaders can act on.","See how IT operations and employee support services perform today, identify the highest-impact gaps, and leave with prioritised next steps and a practical roadmap."]'::jsonb,
